{
  "text": "Imaging evaluation methods were utilized as described in detail in previous publications on the Berlin PRES study [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . In short, MR imaging was performed in all patients. All studies included axial T1-and T2 weighted images.",
